    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "triage_box_t",
      "x": 60, "y": 248,
      "width": 600, "height": 68,
      "text": "Triage Agent (DeepSeek-V3)\n输入: 触发类型(hot/report/surge) + 原始审核摘要 + 当前指标 + 距上次审核时间\n输出: skip (标记已查) 或 review + 建议方向\n成本: 1次LLM，零工具调用",
      "originalText": "Triage Agent (DeepSeek-V3)\n输入: 触发类型(hot/report/surge) + 原始审核摘要 + 当前指标 + 距上次审核时间\n输出: skip (标记已查) 或 review + 建议方向\n成本: 1次LLM，零工具调用",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "strokeColor": "#374151",
