    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "review_box_t",
      "x": 60, "y": 472,
      "width": 600, "height": 95,
      "text": "Review Agent (DeepSeek-V3)\n\n拿到 triage 建议 + 完整原始审核结果 -> 自主取证\n\"原始全绿conf高\" -> mark_checked \"原审置信度高，跳过\"\n\"举报说后段有问题\" -> extract_frames(5, late)  \"50条举报，原审conf 0.55\" -> full_review\n\"热度暴增可能是标题党\" -> review_text + extract_frames(5, even)",
      "originalText": "Review Agent (DeepSeek-V3)\n\n拿到 triage 建议 + 完整原始审核结果 -> 自主取证\n\"原始全绿conf高\" -> mark_checked \"原审置信度高，跳过\"\n\"举报说后段有问题\" -> extract_frames(5, late)  \"50条举报，原审conf 0.55\" -> full_review\n\"热度暴增可能是标题党\" -> review_text + extract_frames(5, even)",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "strokeColor": "#374151",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
